Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.ui.util

This package defines all utility classes to facilitate UI presentation, navigation, and rendering.

          Description

Class Summary
DefaultSettings This class defines a list of default settings for GUI Settings.
SingleFileFilter This class is a basic utility class.
SwingWorker This is courtesy copy from http://gee.cs.oswego.edu/dl/classes/EDU/oswego/cs/dl/util/concurrent/misc/SwingWorker.html

This is the 3rd version of SwingWorker (also known as SwingWorker 3), an abstract class that you subclass to perform GUI-related work in a dedicated thread.
